    <h1>20260421 - LapuLapu ETS Japan, GOCC, and Obs Team</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"5798e76dd94d">Objectives and Key Results</p>
<ul local-id=3D"791ccf3018e6">
<li local-id=3D"659e5589fd2d">
<p local-id=3D"9c14ec3e7844"><strong>Transition App Monitoring and BAU Oper=
ations to GOCC</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a122b959c4d7">
<li local-id=3D"67c8f8700687">
<p local-id=3D"aecc2bab2a84">16 / 65 : 9 in-progress, epos/wodm/solace wait=
ing for access service id. 6 Applications can go live</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"ea17e237e4d5">
<p local-id=3D"ca7833bffcf2"><strong>Dashboards &amp; Tagging (New Relic)</=
strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"c871f7925397">
<li local-id=3D"889a29bdc125">
<p local-id=3D"d7d3e73ae298">Employee Experience Dashboard: 66 / 88. Update=
 from Deb on minion setup (ETA)</p>
<ul local-id=3D"85275e3e952e">
<li local-id=3D"c216ed05d476">
<p local-id=3D"f2812db5990a">Architecture Team maintain cron job to sync na=
ming with LeanIX. Utilize for Silver and Bronze Apps, as well</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"8392ea8fd905">
<p local-id=3D"7c6092a27147">Developer Experience Dashboard: 45 / 60</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"70dc7e0d13bc">
<p local-id=3D"24681ba80138">Japan Business Capability: Add =E2=80=9CAlerts=
: nn=E2=80=9D to specify what the # is counting. Submit to Leadership revie=
w (Hari, Kelvin, Birger) and next steps</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"9479cf1a-e6d2-42b5-8f10-f077f9400619">
<p local-id=3D"fa55e874f5d9"><strong>OMM L2 Application Coverage (Japan)</s=
trong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"50eaa6d1e90a">
<li local-id=3D"39ef0aa058ff">
<p local-id=3D"742c508afa5c">Update from Deb expected early May</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fbfe9afd93c8">
<p local-id=3D"e580a4dbe55b">Kickoff this morning with template showing sco=
pe of monitoring (OMM L2 Entity Mapping) - Japan start verifying immediatel=
y</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"60ababadd877">
<p local-id=3D"a5ad8a2e07bd">Vignesh has list of Japan synthetic monitors -=
 Japan Synthetic Monitors List - sent into Sorting folder, MK and GOCC will=
 review this list</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"9049cc5f2fd8">
<p local-id=3D"174ecc9a8a5b"><strong>Laptop + JPE/JPW Monitoring / Minions<=
/strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"567c375b91ab">
<li local-id=3D"4a5044a7a46a">
<p local-id=3D"df079067e04f">2 laptops delivered, one is working and the ot=
her requires network configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f7ca73f2c54">
<p local-id=3D"61d511c97bd5">New vNET needs to be created and it=E2=80=99s =
being ridiculous</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3c0923574c7b">
<p local-id=3D"c4e29f1b3fb0">Raise another request for existing minions</p>=
</li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"a29c0bf8-a820-44b6-b592-fee21f8fd7b4">
<p local-id=3D"c5bc5a377c5d"><strong>Rapid Recovery enablement</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"dbb7729ed560">
<li local-id=3D"0e1d3706c8c6">
<p local-id=3D"a36a124b9972">Ingenium in-progress</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cebf93aad9c0">
<p local-id=3D"794252cdd11f">As a follow up from =E2=80=9CA bilingual infor=
mation=E2=80=91sharing session with Japan Production Support is required to=
 align on rapid recovery responsibilities and information flow.=E2=80=9C <s=
trong>Rohina </strong>will initiate event in early May for RR explanation s=
ession to PS Team</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"933cf46a1d78"><strong>Credential Management</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"d236c943c75d">
<li local-id=3D"dc733cab5709">
<p local-id=3D"0a0549de57cc">Jesus and team document standards for NR Secur=
e Credentials</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6fcd705539d2">
<p local-id=3D"9e589a97c21d">Workaround is being done for MLK/ePOS/BPM/etc =
applications based on logging into the Portal with a Service ID to access t=
he application endpoint.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"12224feea048">
<li local-id=3D"96b17325d1a5">
<p local-id=3D"98dc1e370237">Notify user if they are using non-standard</p>=
</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
